Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.34,0:00:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,見上げた空に広がる明日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.34,0:00:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs37.5\pos(1204,87.75)}希望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.34,0:00:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}遙望的天空 無垠的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.18,0:00:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,「what's the name?」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.18,0:00:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"what’s the name?"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.01,0:00:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,曖昧な日々に惑う
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.01,0:00:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}在曖昧的日常中不知所措
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.46,0:00:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,立ちすくむような遥かな夢も
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.46,0:00:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}止步不前的話 那遙不可及的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.10,0:00:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,絶望も食らいつくして
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.10,0:00:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}以及絕望都將被吞噬殆盡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.11,0:00:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,願いの形　刻み込む声
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.11,0:00:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}祈願之形 銘刻之聲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.86,0:00:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,もっともっと強く
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.86,0:00:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}更強 更強
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.03,0:00:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,fly high!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.03,0:00:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}fly high!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.04,0:01:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs37.5\pos(1062,993.75)}フィクショソ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.04,0:01:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,まだ誰も知らない想像の向こうで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.04,0:01:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}在無人所及的想像前方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.96,0:01:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,ジリジリと芽生えた衝動的な
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.96,0:01:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}焦躁之中萌發的衝動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.21,0:01:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,skill to stay alive
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.21,0:01:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}skill to stay alive
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.88,0:01:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs37.5\pos(1106,995.75)}リアル
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.88,0:01:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,今感じる全てが現実なら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.88,0:01:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}此刻感到的一切若是現實
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.97,0:01:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,いつか証になるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.97,0:01:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}總有其佐證現身之時
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.97,0:01:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,一つ一つ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.97,0:01:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}一個接一個
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.30,0:01:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs37.5\pos(695,993.75)}キミ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.30,0:01:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,人生を名付けに行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.30,0:01:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs37.5\pos(855,131.25)}你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.30,0:01:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}給人生賦予其名
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.06,0:01:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,(to the east, to the west, to the high)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.06,0:01:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}(東西南北，勇攀高峰)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.97,0:01:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,stand up to the period!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.06,0:01:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,さぁ行こう!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.06,0:01:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}向終點出發吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.76,0:01:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.76,0:01:34.03,Default,Shion,0,0,0,,利姆路大人，該去視察建設工地了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.55,0:01:36.53,Default,Shuna,0,0,0,,我帶你去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.88,0:01:38.29,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,又來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.21,0:01:42.79,Default,Na,0,0,0,,利姆路很困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.79,0:01:47.29,Default,Na,0,0,0,,今天紫苑和朱菜也在爭奪自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.43,0:01:47.29,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1594,1069)}外傳:M的悲劇？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.53,0:01:54.84,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,因為史萊姆的身體抱起來很舒服嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.56,0:01:58.34,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,我有時候也會抱著自己的分身
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.34,0:02:01.86,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,分身 分身之後分給她們不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.86,0:02:03.38,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,啊 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.38,0:02:04.93,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,真要那麼做了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.35,0:02:08.92,Default,Villager,0,0,0,,{\clip(755.185,892.373,755.185,892.373)}也給我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.92,0:02:10.06,Default,Villager,0,0,0,,也請給我一份
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.06,0:02:11.36,Default,Villager,0,0,0,,利姆路大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.36,0:02:12.52,Default,Ranga,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.52,0:02:13.61,Default,Rigurd,0,0,0,,請務必給我...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.52,0:02:17.19,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,會開始一場有別於命名的死亡戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.52,0:02:22.12,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,果然需要這個史萊姆身體的代替品呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.12,0:02:23.91,Default,Text,0,0,0,,{\fnTimes New Roman\b1\c&H000000&\3c&HA6BDCA&\bord12\shad0\fs60\an5\pos(375.999,708)\frx6\fry18\frz3.726}S\Nl\Ni\Nm\Ne
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.47,0:02:23.91,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,木雕史萊姆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.91,0:02:25.58,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,雕塑史萊姆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.58,0:02:27.66,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,金屬製作的金屬史萊姆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.84,0:02:30.52,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,不 應該不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.52,0:02:33.51,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,如果沒有我這樣的柔軟度就沒有意義了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.51,0:02:35.92,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,類似於我身體的...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.92,0:02:36.81,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.79,0:02:40.55,Default,Mikami,0,0,0,,啊...要墮落了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.08,0:02:43.35,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,能讓生物墮落的靠枕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.35,0:02:46.43,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,那東西就觸覺來說應該差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.00,0:02:50.52,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,做個和我一樣的懶人靠枕 其名為 利姆路靠枕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.52,0:02:52.17,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,這不是挺可愛的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.17,0:02:54.15,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,很像抽獎的頭獎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.65,0:02:57.86,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,最大的那個就當作特等獎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.48,0:03:04.20,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,嗯哼 能先放開我一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.20,0:03:05.12,Default,Both,0,0,0,,好 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.41,0:03:11.35,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,我有件事想要拜託朱菜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.35,0:03:13.96,Default,Shuna,0,0,0,,好的 請吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.96,0:03:16.41,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,我有樣東西想做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.57,0:03:21.22,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,如果我說是彈性素材她大概也不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.22,0:03:26.47,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,那個 你能做出滑溜溜還有彈性的布嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.79,0:03:28.93,Default,Shuna,0,0,0,,滑溜溜還有彈性...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.93,0:03:30.74,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,果然不明白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.30,0:03:33.42,Default,Shuna,0,0,0,,是像氨綸一樣的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.42,0:03:34.73,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,居然能明白！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.73,0:03:37.07,Default,Shuna,0,0,0,,憑感覺猜的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.07,0:03:40.07,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,女人的直覺 朱菜你真是個可怕的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.43,0:03:43.82,Default,Shuna,0,0,0,,那個的話很簡單 包在我的身上吧 利姆路大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.82,0:03:45.46,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,好 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.18,0:03:47.79,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,接下來就是填充物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.95,0:03:51.08,Default,Garm,0,0,0,,泡沫塑膠？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.65,0:03:53.58,Default,Garm,0,0,0,,那種材料是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.58,0:03:57.42,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,那個 粒狀的塑膠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.42,0:03:59.26,Default,Garm,0,0,0,,塑膠是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.26,0:04:02.55,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,用發泡聚苯乙烯做的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.97,0:04:05.57,Default,Garm,0,0,0,,發泡聚苯乙烯？？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.57,0:04:08.14,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,發泡聚苯乙烯就是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.14,0:04:08.95,Default,Text,0,0,0,,{\fs90\c&HCDE3E5&}告知
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.35,0:04:12.34,Default,Great Sage,0,0,0,,說明 充氣成型的聚苯乙烯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.54,0:04:13.44,Default,Text,0,0,0,,{\fad(837,1)}聚苯乙烯是合成樹脂的一種
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.87,0:04:16.02,Default,Great Sage,0,0,0,,苯乙烯的聚合物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:17.65,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,嗯 看來說不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.65,0:04:22.90,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,有沒有像是沙子一樣 表面光滑的顆粒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:27.24,Default,Garm,0,0,0,,好像和白沙挺接近的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.24,0:04:28.28,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,白沙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.66,0:04:31.46,Default,Garm,0,0,0,,森林的深處有一處大湖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.46,0:04:34.32,Default,Garm,0,0,0,,我聽說湖心島的沙子就是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.32,0:04:35.83,Default,Garm,0,0,0,,被大自然研磨而成
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.83,0:04:39.59,Default,Garm,0,0,0,,那沙子應該就如同利姆路大人您一樣光滑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.59,0:04:42.09,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,聽起來不錯啊 趕緊去取吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.09,0:04:43.49,Default,Garm,0,0,0,,去取白沙？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.49,0:04:46.76,Default,Garm,0,0,0,,雖然不知道您用來幹嘛 但最好還是不要去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.76,0:04:47.59,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.05,0:04:53.10,Default,Garm,0,0,0,,因為湖裡棲息著魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.10,0:04:54.89,Default,Gabiru,0,0,0,,哇嗚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.89,0:05:00.36,Default,Garm,0,0,0,,如果被抓住了腳的話 最後
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.29,0:05:06.28,Default,Garm,0,0,0,,會被一點一點的拖入水中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.77,0:05:09.18,Default,Garm,0,0,0,,流傳著這樣的傳言
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.29,0:05:14.40,Default,Garm,0,0,0,,嘛對於利姆路大人來說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.40,0:05:17.51,Default,Garm,0,0,0,,就算遇到了魔物也不會出事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.54,0:05:20.40,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,是我杞人憂天了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.40,0:05:22.45,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,那是什麼好恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.90,0:05:24.73,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.73,0:05:28.07,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,這附近應該不會有來襲擊我們的魔物了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.07,0:05:30.89,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,況且我一個人去也會寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.08,0:05:34.72,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,我們一起去取白沙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.72,0:05:37.08,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,順便大家一起去野餐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.05,0:05:40.73,Default,Gobta,0,0,0,,野餐 挺不錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.73,0:05:44.09,Default,Gabiru,0,0,0,,水邊的探索就包在我們身上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.09,0:05:44.65,Default,Lizard,0,0,0,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.65,0:05:45.90,Default,Lizard,0,0,0,,不愧是戈畢魯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.90,0:05:47.03,Default,Lizard,0,0,0,,真帥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.03,0:05:56.85,Default,Lizards,0,0,0,,{\pos(970,83)}戈畢魯 戈畢魯...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.95,0:05:52.28,Default,Soka,0,0,0,,好吵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.28,0:05:55.81,Default,Shuna,0,0,0,,能和利姆路大人同去遠定我真的很高興呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.81,0:05:58.79,Default,Ranga,0,0,0,,如果是主人 我願意追隨到天涯海角
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.15,0:06:01.09,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,我都說了只是去湖邊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.52,0:06:03.88,Default,Shion,0,0,0,,您要用白沙來做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.88,0:06:06.89,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,你們就期待我完工吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.37,0:06:11.39,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,要把禮物內容透露給收禮的人還真有點...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.78,0:06:12.97,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,話說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:17.96,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,把事情和這些對沒興趣的男人們說了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.96,0:06:21.48,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,話說 利格魯德好像很想要的樣子還是對他保密吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.32,0:06:29.24,Default,Beni,0,0,0,,請務必讓我們協助
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.26,0:06:32.51,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,紅丸你還挺有幹勁的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.51,0:06:33.37,Default,Beni,0,0,0,,那是當然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.81,0:06:37.87,Default,Beni,0,0,0,,以利姆路大人為原型做的靠枕 得到它的紫苑一定會很珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.87,0:06:41.58,Default,Beni,0,0,0,,隨身攜帶並且還會注意不要弄髒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.58,0:06:44.71,Default,Beni,0,0,0,,也就是說 紫苑再也不會接近廚房了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.32,0:06:50.47,Default,Gobta,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.47,0:06:52.38,Default,Beni,0,0,0,,這任務可事關重大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.38,0:06:53.23,Default,Souei,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.23,0:06:55.70,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,說實話我根本沒那麼想過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.70,0:06:59.85,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,畢竟他們很久之前就知道紫苑的料理有多麼的恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.85,0:07:03.23,Default,Hakurou,0,0,0,,老身也去 利姆路大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.99,0:07:09.83,Default,Gobta,0,0,0,,師 師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.83,0:07:11.49,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,連白老也
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.30,0:07:17.85,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,就這樣在各種意義上值得期待的野餐開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.72,0:07:23.95,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,總感覺有點在意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.95,0:07:26.75,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,住在湖裡的魔物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.09,0:07:31.01,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,如果只是傳言還好 要是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.51,0:07:39.52,Default,Shuna,0,0,0,,真美
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.52,0:07:41.06,Default,Shion,0,0,0,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.54,0:07:44.81,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,這裡像就是葛洛姆所說的湖了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.81,0:07:47.82,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,也就是說白沙所在的地方就是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.21,0:07:50.13,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,那個地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.13,0:07:53.32,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,我還想著湖有多恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.23,0:07:56.17,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,不是也挺漂亮的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.19,0:08:00.17,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,好 在去取白沙之前先填飽肚子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.17,0:08:01.08,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,, 吃午餐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:03.19,Default,All,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.23,0:08:26.31,Default,Gabiru,0,0,0,,這還真是不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.31,0:08:29.68,Default,Soka,0,0,0,,兄長大人 那份玉子燒是要給蒼影大人的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.68,0:08:30.23,Default,Gabiru,0,0,0,,美味
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.06,0:08:38.62,Default,Shion,0,0,0,,利姆路大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.62,0:08:39.74,Default,Shion,0,0,0,,請吃便當
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.33,0:08:41.79,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,便當
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.57,0:08:44.96,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,沒能阻止她嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:48.29,Default,Beni,0,0,0,,您不是說便當自備嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.29,0:08:51.13,Default,Hakurou,0,0,0,,與我無關
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.41,0:08:55.51,Default,Shion,0,0,0,,我原本做了便當 可是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.51,0:08:56.34,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.34,0:08:59.10,Default,Shion,0,0,0,,因為這個盛器的強度不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.10,0:09:00.98,Default,Shion,0,0,0,,所以漏了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.48,0:09:09.23,Default,Shion,0,0,0,,看來裝不下我對利姆路大人的心意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.23,0:09:12.76,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,裝不下的話那就沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.76,0:09:13.73,Default,Shion,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.88,0:09:21.83,Default,Shion,0,0,0,,作為替代我做了這個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.49,0:09:24.54,Default,Shion,0,0,0,,飯糰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.16,0:09:30.04,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,這是什麼新型魔物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.04,0:09:31.77,Default,Shion,0,0,0,,來請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.77,0:09:34.38,Default,Shion,0,0,0,,我向哥布一請教過料理的秘訣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.75,0:09:36.13,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,秘...秘訣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.13,0:09:39.80,Default,Shion,0,0,0,,沒錯 被告知了最重要的是傾注愛情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.17,0:09:43.31,Default,Shion,0,0,0,,這是我傾注了很多愛情所做的飯糰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.35,0:09:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(485,1)\c&HCC08AE&}咕咕咕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.66,0:09:50.11,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.52,0:09:52.27,Default,Shion,0,0,0,,那麼利姆路大人請
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.61,0:10:03.12,Default,Shion,0,0,0,,快攔下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.69,0:10:05.47,Default,Gabiru,0,0,0,,紫苑下做的飯糰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.47,0:10:07.01,Default,Gabiru,0,0,0,,吾輩來攔住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.89,0:10:10.04,Default,Text,0,0,0,,{\fad(485,1)\c&HCC08AE&}咕咕咕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.04,0:10:11.71,Default,Gabiru,0,0,0,,那是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.85,0:10:24.70,Default,Text,0,0,0,,{\fad(485,1)\c&HCC08AE&}咕咕咕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.81,0:10:29.31,Default,Lizard,0,0,0,,超帥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.31,0:10:30.26,Default,Lizard,0,0,0,,那是當然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.26,0:10:31.52,Default,Lizard,0,0,0,,戈畢魯大人 滿分
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.52,0:10:35.17,Default,Lizards,0,0,0,,戈畢魯 戈畢魯 戈畢魯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.22,0:10:49.27,Default,Lizard,0,0,0,,戈畢魯大人 死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.27,0:10:51.12,Default,Lizard,0,0,0,,這也沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.12,0:10:53.17,Default,Lizard,0,0,0,,一臉安祥 好帥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.17,0:10:56.51,Default,Shion,0,0,0,,真是非常抱歉 給利姆大人的食物居然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.51,0:11:00.23,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,沒事 沒事 你看我就算不吃也沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.23,0:11:02.18,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,沒事的 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.18,0:11:05.81,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,比起這個 快去做下水的準備吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.81,0:11:07.35,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,去取白沙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.83,0:11:13.19,Default,Na,0,0,0,,所謂的準備就是去換泳裝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.19,0:11:16.77,Default,Na,0,0,0,,矮人們用氨綸做了泳裝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.67,0:11:27.95,Default,Shion,0,0,0,,利姆路大人 感覺如何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.07,0:11:34.96,Default,Shuna,0,0,0,,稍微有點害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.62,0:11:51.73,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,泳裝是我設計 葛洛姆他們一同完成的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.73,0:11:55.23,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,做得好啊 矮人三兄弟 讚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.69,0:11:57.69,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,各位都很合適呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.06,0:11:58.94,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,然後
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.20,0:12:09.45,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,為什麼連你們也穿著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.93,0:12:10.79,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.53,0:12:13.54,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,不妙 嵐加好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.23,0:12:17.13,Default,Shuna,0,0,0,,葛洛姆說也為利姆路準備了泳裝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.84,0:12:19.59,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,我也有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.41,0:12:21.30,Default,Shuna,0,0,0,,就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:22.59,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,死庫水
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.40,0:12:26.09,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,不行不行，這絕對不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.63,0:12:29.35,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,葛洛姆你們幾個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.10,0:12:33.21,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,嘛 這樣倒也還行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.21,0:12:35.70,Default,Beni,0,0,0,,那 差不多該動身了 利姆路大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.70,0:12:37.60,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,說的也是呢 那大家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.60,0:12:39.36,Default,Milim,0,0,0,,給我等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.81,0:12:49.79,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,蜜莉姆？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.52,0:12:53.70,Default,Milim,0,0,0,,好過分 為什麼野餐不叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.70,0:12:54.96,Default,Milim,0,0,0,,明明是死黨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.96,0:12:56.17,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.49,0:13:00.92,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,怕會發生什麼麻煩的事情 這樣的話根本說不出囗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.92,0:13:03.55,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,啊抱歉 我以為你很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.55,0:13:07.18,Default,Milim,0,0,0,,即使再忙 死黨的邀請我也會隨時趕來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.18,0:13:09.43,Default,Milim,0,0,0,,那麼 你們現在要去幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.43,0:13:11.52,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,游去湖心島
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.52,0:13:13.72,Default,Milim,0,0,0,,要游泳嗎 那我也要游
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.72,0:13:15.93,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,你沒帶泳裝來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.92,0:13:21.16,Default,Milim,0,0,0,,根本不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.91,0:13:21.15,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,不行 不行 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.15,0:13:22.68,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,絕對不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.68,0:13:24.67,Default,Milim,0,0,0,,真是麻煩的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.67,0:13:25.49,Default,Milim,0,0,0,,看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.62,0:13:34.76,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.76,0:13:35.87,Default,Milim,0,0,0,,泳裝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.72,0:13:38.38,Default,Great Sage,0,0,0,,說明
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.74,0:13:41.63,Default,Great Sage,0,0,0,,雖然設計相同但材質不同
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.63,0:13:46.38,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,好像可以但又感覺不太行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.06,0:13:51.89,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,好的 大家 葛洛姆所說湖心島就有白沙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.23,0:13:54.15,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,傳聞其中也有魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.15,0:13:55.85,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,各位行動要多加小心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.85,0:13:56.89,Default,All,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.21,0:13:59.94,Default,Milim,0,0,0,,魔物什麼的隨出來也沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.94,0:14:03.81,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,喂無論出現什麼 你也絕對不能動手喲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.81,0:14:07.80,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,你會把這附近都毀掉的 約好了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.31,0:14:09.78,Default,Milim,0,0,0,,我明白啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.28,0:14:15.42,Default,Milim,0,0,0,,好涼快呀 好舒服呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.42,0:14:17.32,Default,Gobta,0,0,0,,真的很舒服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.32,0:14:19.42,Default,Gabiru,0,0,0,,讓我想起故鄉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.33,0:14:30.27,Default,Beni,0,0,0,,並沒有感受到什麼強大的氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.27,0:14:32.20,Default,Beni,0,0,0,,關於魔物的傳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.20,0:14:37.10,Default,Beni,0,0,0,,可能只是溺水的事件被加油添醋傳出來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.10,0:14:41.51,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,如果是那樣就好了 不過注意點沒什麼壞處
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.23,0:14:43.02,Default,Shion,0,0,0,,利姆路大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.16,0:14:51.51,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,我的腳好像被海藻之類的東西纏住了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.60,0:15:23.44,Default,Shuna,0,0,0,,不 不要 這是什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.44,0:15:26.12,Default,Shion,0,0,0,,利 利姆路大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.44,0:15:28.94,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,朱菜 紫苑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.39,0:15:31.22,Default,Soka,0,0,0,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.94,0:15:38.04,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,看起來好色情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.54,0:15:47.55,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,色情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.55,0:15:50.72,Default,Milim,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.72,0:15:51.88,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,水刃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.95,0:15:58.72,Default,Beni,0,0,0,,利姆路是大人的斬擊居然無效
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.81,0:16:17.03,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,這就是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.66,0:16:20.85,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,魔物的本體嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.76,0:16:25.54,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,喂 能聽到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.81,0:16:34.24,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,上面的同伴很困擾 能停下來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:38.97,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,它的攻擊很魯莽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.62,0:16:41.43,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,這不像是攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.43,0:16:43.75,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,更像是在痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.75,0:16:45.94,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,這傢伙到底發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.44,0:16:51.48,Default,Text,0,0,0,,{\3c&H291517&\pos(660,60)\c&HCC08AE&}咕咕咕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.57,0:16:55.28,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,居然吃了這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.62,0:17:04.54,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,所以才暴走了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.11,0:17:08.29,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,畢竟這個等級的魔物也不常見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.95,0:17:12.05,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,等一下我現在就讓你解脫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.58,0:17:21.83,Default,Shuna,0,0,0,,動作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:24.02,Default,Beni,0,0,0,,停下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.49,0:17:25.52,Default,Beni,0,0,0,,難道是利姆路大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.09,0:17:38.53,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,好 已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:44.37,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,你在找我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.08,0:17:48.36,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,你難不成看不見周圍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.01,0:17:51.46,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,那麼照我說的做做看？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.46,0:17:54.13,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,有個叫「魔力感知」的技能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.97,0:17:58.34,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,在這種地方孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.34,0:18:01.07,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,而且還什麼都看不見
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.07,0:18:04.89,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,我能明白你喲 因為我最初也是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.40,0:18:07.54,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,我和那傢伙都很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.54,0:18:10.75,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,所以無論是史萊姆 還是 巨大的龍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.75,0:18:11.90,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,也成為了朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.23,0:18:15.52,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,在那之後我不再孤獨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.52,0:18:17.90,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,接受了許多委託
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.90,0:18:22.20,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,但結果都是因為我害怕寂寞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.06,0:18:27.62,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,哦 看來你看得見了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.36,0:18:32.04,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,乖 那我差不多該走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.22,0:18:36.88,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,露骨地顯示出寂寞了 和某條龍—樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.25,0:18:41.30,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,那個 我想要湖心島的沙子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.30,0:18:43.89,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,所以今後會三不五時來取
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.41,0:18:48.74,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,很快就會再來見你的 所以別那麼寂寞了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.80,0:19:03.70,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,抱歉 讓大家擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.70,0:19:06.07,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,我和魔物談妥了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.84,0:19:08.57,Default,Shuna,0,0,0,,利姆路大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.57,0:19:09.96,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.13,0:19:29.48,Default,Shion,0,0,0,,利姆路大人 請讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.48,0:19:32.73,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,等一下 這裡面有很深的誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.71,0:19:35.73,Default,Shion,0,0,0,,暴走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.73,0:19:39.24,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,因為某種原因他得到了很強大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.24,0:19:41.11,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,所以暫時暴走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.50,0:19:43.67,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,給我個面子放過他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.25,0:19:46.04,Default,Shion,0,0,0,,那沒辦法了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.12,0:19:49.87,Default,Shion,0,0,0,,但是 為什麼會暴走呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.21,0:19:53.19,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,誰知道 為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.02,0:19:57.63,Default,Text,0,0,0,,{\3c&H34001E&\pos(1650,120)\c&HCC08AE&}咕咕咕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.63,0:19:59.55,Default,Text,0,0,0,,{\3c&H8F5861&\pos(960,60)\c&HCC08AE&}咕咕咕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.63,0:20:06.15,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,那個...那個 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.15,0:20:09.56,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,咦我們腳下的沙子超級滑溜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.33,0:20:12.03,Default,Shion,0,0,0,,照你這麼一說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.03,0:20:14.56,Default,Beni,0,0,0,,是呢 難道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.95,0:20:16.90,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,滑溜溜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.90,0:20:18.40,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,這就是白沙了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.06,0:20:22.61,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,滑溜溜 滑溜溜的白沙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.79,0:20:28.62,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,這個沙子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.30,0:20:31.51,Default,Great Sage,0,0,0,,包含了大量水分的沙子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.51,0:20:34.12,Default,Great Sage,0,0,0,,被魔物的黏液所研磨而成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.11,0:20:36.79,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,果然是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.94,0:20:41.61,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,因為這傢伙棲息在這附近 所以形成了這些沙子的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.08,0:20:45.55,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,好 這裡的沙子我們都拿走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.88,0:20:48.79,Default,Shion,0,0,0,,欸？我們帶的袋子不夠裝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.79,0:20:52.43,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,不用一次全部拿走 我們三不五時來現就行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.01,0:20:52.43,Default,Milim,0,0,0,,{\an8}滑溜溜 滑溜溜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.24,0:20:56.89,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,雖然能夠全部裝到胃袋裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.89,0:20:59.19,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,不過和這傢伙還有約定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.88,0:21:01.73,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,還會再來玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.76,0:21:12.07,Default,Shion,0,0,0,,今天我做了能夠恢復精神的料理
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.07,0:21:15.58,Default,Shuna,0,0,0,,不 偶爾也嚐一下我親手做的飯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.49,0:21:19.38,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,那個 靠枕已經不要了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.38,0:21:23.01,Default,Shuna,0,0,0,,要的 我會帶回去好好使用的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.01,0:21:25.38,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,不，那個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.01,0:21:30.13,Default,Beni,0,0,0,,還是比不過真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.10,0:21:35.21,Default,Shion,0,0,0,,照顧利姆路大人也是我重要的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.21,0:21:38.10,Default,Shuna,0,0,0,,太狡猾了請讓我也一起照顧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.79,0:21:42.11,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,啊 真是的 隨她們便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.11,0:21:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.34,0:22:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼 只持有唯一的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.34,0:22:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5}どうして　希望を持つひとだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.91,0:22:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,內心只知道絕望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.91,0:22:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5}心に　絶望を知るのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.70,0:22:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼 只持有唯一的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.70,0:22:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5}どうして　勇気を持つひとだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.62,0:22:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,名譽的盡頭 只是傷痕累累
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.62,0:22:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5}名誉の果てに　傷を負うのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.46,0:22:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,對於悲傷的事物 不願低頭面對
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.46,0:22:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5}悲しい出来事に　目を伏せたくなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.09,0:22:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,全新的黎明 被稱為夢想之物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.09,0:22:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5}新しい夜明けを　夢と名付けてみせた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.74,0:22:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,扭曲的夜晚之間 降下了光明
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.74,0:22:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5}ねじれた　夜の隙間に　光がおちる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.40,0:22:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,連上天都哭泣了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.40,0:22:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5}空が泣いているよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.40,0:22:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,世界的盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.40,0:22:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5}世界の果て
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.99,0:22:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麼 雖然不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.99,0:22:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5}なんて　知らないけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.07,0:22:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,這雙手所觸及的地方 我想守護
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.07,0:22:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5}この手が届く場所は　守りたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.75,0:23:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,戰鬥的理由 僅凝視唯一一點
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.75,0:23:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5}戦う理由　ひとつ　睨みつけた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.00,0:23:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,作為能夠彼此諒解的答案 我們
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.00,0:23:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5}許しあうことの　答えになる　僕らは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.26,0:23:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,絕不認輸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.26,0:23:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5}負けちゃいけない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.75,0:23:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,
